Package: system-analyser
Architecture: armhf arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgtk-3-0
Description: Lightweight real-time system monitor for Raspberry Pi
 A GTK3-based monitoring tool displaying CPU usage, temperature, memory,
 and system metrics with CSV logging capabilities. Open-source and
 community-driven development.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time CPU usage and temperature monitoring
  - Memory and swap usage tracking
  - System uptime and load average display
  - CPU clock speed and voltage monitoring
  - Data logging to CSV files
